    • classValidation

      public FitnessClass classValidation(String isClass, String instructor, String location)
      method that takes user input and checks whetehr or not the class detailed by input corresponds to a real class in the class schedule. If the class queried is a real class, method will return a reference to the class in the ClassSchedule object. Otherwise, it will return null.
      Parameters:
      isClass - type of class being queried
      instructor - instructor for the class
      location - location at which class is taking place
      Returns:
      If the class exists in ClassSchedule return reference to the class, else return null

      private void importMembers()
      Imports historical member information from the text file named memberList.txt located in the source directory This method assumes that all historical members hav valid member information, therefore forgoing new member information validation.
